description: This is an interactive dataset that provides an alphabetical listing of all the data views in the Health.Data.NY.gov catalog.  In the "Name" column, if you click on the name of the data view, it will take you directly to the data view.  Also displayed is the description, keywords, custom meta data notes, column names and date last updated.
